Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:06.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Asking someone how long they believed in Santa Claus...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:10.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}...is so meaningless that it couldn't even serve as worthless gossip...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:15.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Regardless, if you're going to ask me how much of my childhood I spent believing in an old man in a red suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:17.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}...I can confidently say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.23,0:00:19.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}...I never believed in him in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:25.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew that the Santa at the preschool Christmas event was just a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:29.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I didn't even have to see Mommy kissing Santa Claus...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:34.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I suppose I was just a precocious child who questioned the existence of an old man who only worked on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:35.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:38.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be it aliens, time travelers, ghosts, demons, espers...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:42.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...or evil organizations and the heroes out of cartoons or comic books who battle them...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.51,0:00:46.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't realize that they weren't real until some time later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.36,0:00:49.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No. I had probably already realized the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.37,0:00:51.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just didn't want to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.59,0:00:56.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Deep in my heart, I wished that aliens, time travelers, ghosts, demons, espers...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.01,0:00:59.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...or evil organizations might pop up in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:02.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, reality is rather cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:06.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One must admire how well the laws of physics were written.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:10.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At some point, I stopped being glued to TV UFO specials and programs on psychics.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:12.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aliens. Time travelers. Espers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:13.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}None of those could possibly exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.93,0:01:16.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Though I kind of wish they did...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:19.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I suppose my ability to hold convictions while accepting reality is a sign that I've matured.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:20.67,HaruhiSignSerif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0.1\3a&H00&\3c&H110000&\be1\b1\fs32\c&H434033&\pos(443,350)}Entrance\nCeremony
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:24.68,HaruhiNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H66&\fscx90\frx-20\fry-60\frz-55\1c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\fs20\pos(318,389)}Entrance\nCeremony
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:24.68,HaruhiNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1a&H84&\fscx90\frx-15\fry-65\frz-55\1c&HFFE4E4&\bord0\fs20\pos(197,342)}9:30 am
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:25.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I graduated from middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:28.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I also graduated from those childish dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:30.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and became accustomed to the routine of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:33.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so I entered high school with no particular vision in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:35.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I hope to have a good year with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:35.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.36,0:01:40.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,From East Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.63,0:01:42.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruhi Suzumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.44,0:01:44.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in ordinary humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:50.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If there are any aliens, time travelers, sliders, or espers here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.25,0:01:52.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...come join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:53.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:57.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are we supposed to laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.31,0:02:01.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A striking beauty stood before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:12.13,HaruhiNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFEEEE\1a&H99\pos(437,50)}Okabe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:13.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, whoever's next.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Most people would think that she was just joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:15.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}From East Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:16.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm Taniguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:20.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In hindsight, that was neither a joke nor a laughing matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.05,0:02:21.84,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruhi was always dead serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:25.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:26.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I deeply hope that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:28.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I can believe it was mere coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:06.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as Haruhi Suzumiya was sitting still with her mouth shut...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:08.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...one would believe that she was just a beautiful high schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:11.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And since my seat just happened to be located right in front of hers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:13.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I figured it might be acceptable to approach her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:16.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can't blame me for losing my mind for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:18.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:20.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,About the stuff in that introduction earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.66,0:04:22.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How much of it was serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:25.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What stuff earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The stuff about aliens and whatnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:30.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:31.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:34.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:36.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:37.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:43.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:45.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't learn until later on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:48.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that they were all from the same middle school as Haruhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:51.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're interested in her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:52.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I won't mince words.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:53.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:58.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I was in the same class as her for three years in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Her queerness takes a path unlike anything you've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean her introduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:03.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:07.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She did a bunch of strange things back in middle school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:10.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The most famous one would be the campus grounds graffiti incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:11.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:14.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's this device that uses lime to draw white lines, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:15.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it called again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:16.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:20.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone used that to draw some huge pictograph on the grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:22.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was secretly done at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:25.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember seeing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that in the local section of the newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:31.34,HaruhiSignSerif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H111111&\1a&HFF&\3a&&H55&\bord1\fs22\frz22\pos(192,35)}The Tanabata Mystery
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:31.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like a failed attempt at a Nazca etching.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:34.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And she was the one who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:36.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She said so herself, so it's gotta be her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:41.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,One morning, we showed up at the classroom to find all the desks out in the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:44.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She drew stars on the roof in paint...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:47.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She even stuck a bunch of talismans all around school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:47.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.87,0:05:50.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the ones they use to reanimate corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:52.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea what for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:55.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, she's pretty popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:56.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she does have looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.57,0:06:01.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And then she's athletic and probably gets better grades than most.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:05.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't tell she's a freak when she's just standing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:07.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any stories about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:10.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,For a while, she kept going from one to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:12.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As far as I know, the longest lasted a week...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:18.30,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and apparently the shortest was five minutes after she agreed to go out with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:21.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to deal with ordinary humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't agree to go out in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:27.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a story I heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:28.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:31.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but apparently she doesn't turn anyone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:35.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm warning you before you get any weird ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:37.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:39.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's nothing to give up on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:40.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not even interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Personally, I'd say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:47.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...the best one in the class is her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:51.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoko Asakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:54.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gotta be in the top three for our year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:58.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you check out all the first-year girls or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:06:59.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:01.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I assigned them ranks from A to D...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:04.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I learned the full names of the ones who ranked A.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:06.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And Asakura-san is an A?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,An AA+.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's definitely a nice person, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:16.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.82,0:07:21.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At this point, Haruhi Suzumiya had yet to act up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:24.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And for me, it was a month of relaxation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:26.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, I should note that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:29.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I observed a number of Haruhi's eccentric behaviors during this period.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:33.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, peculiarity number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:35.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her hairstyle changes everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:36.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:37.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:38.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:38.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thursday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:39.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:42.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As the days progressed, the number of tied-off points in her hair would increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:46.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After resetting on Monday, it would increase one a day until Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what her head looks like on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd sure like to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:54.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Peculiarity number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:55.22,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}They saw my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:57.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boys and girls split up for gym class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:59.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Girls change in odd-numbered rooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:02.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and boys move to even-numbered rooms, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...ignoring the fact that boys were still present...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:06.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...she began taking off her uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:17.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It would appear that she viewed guys on the same level as potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:20.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Peculiarity number three.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:23.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To my amazement...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:24.02,HaruhiNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\b1\be1\frz7\c&H4B8F85&\pos(300,82)}Tea Ceremony Club
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:28.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...she temporarily joined a wide range of clubs in this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:31.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So... Why not join permanently?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:31.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All the sports clubs without exception fervently pursued her membership.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:34.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}'Sides, your presence alone would motivate us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:36.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Turning their requests down, she would arbitrarily join a different club every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:39.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the end, she didn't join a single one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:41.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What exactly is she trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:49.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the process, we reached the first day after Golden Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:51.59,HaruhiCaption,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}[Golden Week: A week long holiday encompassing four national holidays.]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000000&}- Yo, Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:51.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:54.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Incidentally, Kyon is my nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Did you go somewhere for Golden Week?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I took my sister to see our grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:57.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I sure wish people would stop calling me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:57.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:58.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,'Sup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:03.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So that makes today Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:05.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And with that thought in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:07.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was probably possessed by some demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:09.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can think of no other explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:13.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you change your hair every day as an alien countermeasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:16.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I talked to Haruhi Suzumiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:17.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:20.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:24.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:28.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...each day gives off a different image.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:31.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Color-wise, Monday(Moon) would be yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}I get the feeling this is the first time we've had a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:32.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Tuesday(Fire) would be red.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:33.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wednesday(Water) would be blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thursday(Wood) would be green.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:36.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Friday(Gold) is gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:37.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Saturday(Earth) is light brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:39.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunday(Sun) is white.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:41.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can see where she's coming from, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:43.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So with numbers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:46.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...Monday would be zero and Sunday would be six?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:50.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Monday feels more like one to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:53.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody asked for your opinion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:12.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Have I met you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:13.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:14.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:17.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The trigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:20.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...while being nothing particularly significant...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:23.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This would indeed be the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:26.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In any case, a serious response from Haruhi was a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:29.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Shut up!" "Moron!" "Be quiet!" "Who cares about that!?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:31.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...were the replies I was expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which is why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:37.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...when Haruhi showed up with her long hair cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:39.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I was rather disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:44.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyway, isn't cutting it the day after I point it out a bit hasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:44.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:47.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:50.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:54.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}...conversing with Haruhi in the short period before homeroom became a daily event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:54.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard this rumor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:57.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that you've dumped every guy you went out with?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:01.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives you the right to ask me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:05.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you've heard, but very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:06.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably all true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:11.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't a single guy you seriously wanted to date?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:12.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,All of them were totally no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:15.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Every single one of them was ridiculously square.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:19.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,None of them were aliens, time travelers, or espers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:20.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:24.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's up with most of them asking me out over the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:26.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Important matters like these should be said in person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:28.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:30.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}I'll just go along with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.71,0:11:30.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd probably call her out somewhere and tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:33.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not important!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:34.83,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So is it or isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:40.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is that there are only worthless men on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:43.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent most of middle school being irritated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:46.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what kind of a guy did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:47.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm guessing an alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:48.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,An alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:51.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Or something along those lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.15,0:11:54.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, as long as it isn't an ordinary human, it doesn't matter if it's a guy or a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:58.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so particular about non-humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that more fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:14.38,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:17.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of magic did you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:18.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:22.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen Suzumiya talk that long before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:24.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:25.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:29.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I get the feeling I just asked whatever was on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:30.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:34.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon's always liked weird girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:36.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say things that'll cause misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd also like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:43.78,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzumiya-san never responds no matter how hard I try to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get her to talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:46.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a trick to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.78,0:12:51.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm relieved now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:55.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be worried if Suzumiya-san kept isolating herself from the rest of the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:58.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good thing that she's managed to make a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:12:59.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:05.02,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep up whatever you're doing to make Suzumiya-san open up to the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:07.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We were fortunate enough to be put into the same class...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:09.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so we should all be friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:10.36,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:11.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Easy for you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:13.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If I need to tell her anything from now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:16.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll ask you to tell her for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:18.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:21.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not her spokesman or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.44,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:33.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:35.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're buddies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:37.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm surrounded by a bunch of idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:39.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our seating arrangements are being changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:42.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After drawing my lot from the tin...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.56,0:13:46.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...my new seat was next to the window, second from behind. Quite excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.56,0:13:44.56,HaruhiNote,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\bord0\fry-40\1c&HF0DDDD\1a&H99&\3a&H99&\frz-2\fs18\pos(599,72)}Seating\narrangement\nchange
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.54,0:13:47.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Farewell, Haruhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:51.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is coincidence, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:56.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really try joining all the clubs?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:58.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know if you find one that's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:01.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There totally aren't any at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An immediate response.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:03.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Totally none at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:06.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It appears she has a habit of using the word "totally."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:10.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was expecting something better after entering high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:13.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but this is no different from back during mandatory education.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.08,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I went to the wrong school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:18.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What criteria are you using to choose a school?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:21.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a Mystery Research Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:22.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:24.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:27.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't had a single encounter with anything like a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:30.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,All the members are just mystery fanatic bookworms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:32.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,None of them look like detective material.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:33.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:36.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I was expecting more from the Supernatural Phenomena Research Society...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:39.70,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it was just a bunch of occult freaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:40.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:41.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:44.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:47.62,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,With so many clubs, you'd think there'd be at least one weird one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:50.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do anything about what doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:54.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, humans have to settle for what's in front of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:57.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about it, the humans who were unable to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:14:59.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...made discoveries or inventions...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:01.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...and advanced civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:04.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Planes were invented because people wanted to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:07.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Cars and trains came to be because people wanted easier means to move around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:12.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this came from a limited number of people who had innovative plans and concepts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:15.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, geniuses made it all possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:20.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Common folk like us are best off living an ordinary life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:21.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:26.04,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.04,0:15:28.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This conversation gave her the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:32.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It happened suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.92,0:15:38.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:39.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:41.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Figured out what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:45.09,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't I realize such a simple thing sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:45.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Realize what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:48.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If there isn't one, I just have to make it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:49.31,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Make what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A club!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:55.37,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:56.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just calm down for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:58.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with your reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:16:01.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be a little happier about this discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:03.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in class right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Clubroom... Clubroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:14.46,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Assist me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:17.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This feels like extortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:18.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Assist you with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:20.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Making my new club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:24.47,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to help you with your idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:25.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me that first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:29.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go secure a room and members...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:31.89,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so you go get the chartering paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:31.33,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}She's not listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:34.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of club are you planning on making?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:36.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does that even matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:38.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Making the club comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.05,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:41.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Find out what you have to do before school's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:43.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find a room before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:44.48,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:48.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The provisions for chartering a "student association":
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:51.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Five members or more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:52.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A faculty advisor...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.97,0:16:53.66,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a club name...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:54.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a chairperson...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:56.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...a summary of club activities...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There was no need to find out anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:01.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything is listed out on the back of the student handbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't mind writing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:04.77,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but I'm willing to bet that whatever Haruhi has in mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:09.43,HaruhiSignSerif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs26\frx5\fry-1\frz-61\move(694,123,651,147)}The provisions for chartering a "student association":
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:09.43,HaruhiSignSerif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs26\frx5\fry-1\frz-63.7\move(578,223,535,247)}Determine faculty advisor, name, responsible party, and club activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:09.43,HaruhiSignSerif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\be1\fs27\frx12\fry-4\frz-65.1\move(475,210,432,234)}must adhere to the policy of leading a productive and creative school life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:09.43,HaruhiSignSerif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\be1\fs27\frx14\fry-6\frz-67.1\move(370,183,327,207)}activities and performance, a motion for a raise in status to "research society"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.68,0:17:09.43,HaruhiSignSerif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\be1\fs26\frx14\fry-7\frz-69.3\move(272,163,229,187)}as long as the group remains a student association, no funding will be provided.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:09.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...isn't going to "adhere to the policy of leading a productive and creative school life."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:11.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Hol—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:11.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What! Not aga—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:16.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This room is now our clubroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:17.17,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a tick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:18.27,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:21.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The arts department's clubhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:25.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The art club and wind ensemble have an art room and a music room, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:29.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Clubs and associations that don't have such special classrooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:31.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...have rooms in this clubhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:32.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Also known as the old shack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:34.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the literary club's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:36.21,HaruhiSignSerif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\3a&H99\fs24\frz3.8\fry-10\bord0.2\3c&H000000&\pos(300,141)}Literary Club
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:36.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So this belongs to the literary club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:40.56,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But the third-years all graduated last spring so it has zero members.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:45.03,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the only club that would have been cut if nobody new joined.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:48.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And this girl is the first-year who joined.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:51.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the club wasn't cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:52.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:54.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:55.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:57.72,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she's fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:02.13,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When I asked her to lend me this room during lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:03.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...she said go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:05.18,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't care as long as she can read apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:09.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you could call her an oddball.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah. You're one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:14.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki Nagato.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:17.65,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Nagato-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:21.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's planning on turning this room into an I-have-no-idea-what club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:22.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that still okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:23.59,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:25.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:27.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll probably be a huge bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:28.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:31.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You might even get chased out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:32.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:38.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to meet in this room after school from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:40.23,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You better show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:42.73,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, heads will roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:44.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:46.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I like my head where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:48.45,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to recruit members first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:50.99,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We need at least two more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:52.41,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:55.43,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...you've already counted in that literary club girl as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:58.50,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aren't you confusing her with a piece of furniture that came with the room now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:00.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find them in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:03.71,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I happen to know of someone made for this club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:05.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:07.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:11.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:12.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:14.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I shuffled my feet towards the clubroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:15.85,HaruhiSignSerif,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\be1\3a&H99\fs30\frz-15\frx-20\fry-15\fscy110\bord0.2\3c&H000000&\pos(591,234)}Literary Club
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.39,0:19:17.98,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:21.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:25.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:26.82,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Which part of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:29.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:31.86,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You like books, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:35.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Relatively.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:36.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:41.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can I leave now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.90,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Sorry about being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:47.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It took a while to catch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:49.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was another girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:51.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And an extraordinarily beautiful one at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:51.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:54.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:57.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:20:00.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you l-locking the door!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:01.19,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:02.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:05.68,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:07.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mikuru Asahina-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:12.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the whole introduction?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:15.35,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you abduct her from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:16.85,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't abduct her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:18.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It was voluntary arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:19.34,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:22.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught her daydreaming in a second-year classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:26.93,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I go through every corner of the school during breaks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:29.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I remembered her after spotting her a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.39,0:20:33.12,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was wondering why she wasn't in the classroom during breaks... So that's what she was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:36.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... isn't she an upperclassman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:38.61,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:40.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.21,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Asahina-san, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:44.00,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:45.49,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:49.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's super cute, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:52.26,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She sounded like a dangerous kidnapper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:55.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that turn-ons are an essential factor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:57.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:20:58.76,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:20:59.67,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn-ons! Turn-ons!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:02.28,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an element of turning people on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:06.14,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fundamentally, in every story where something strange happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:09.64,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's always an alluring, lolita-looking character present.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.98,0:21:14.54,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:19.15,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so small yet, look.
