Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.91,0:21:22.79,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A lolita face with big breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.79,0:21:25.51,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an important element of turning people on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:26.16,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}News to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:28.63,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They really are big...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:30.58,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting to piss me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:33.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a cute face is sporting bigger ones than me!
