Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:36.92,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:37.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you touch them?
