Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:42.06,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:47.55,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that this Asahina-san is cute, small, and has big breasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.55,0:21:48.80,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...is why you brought her here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:50.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:51.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She must have been born dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:55.42,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I figure we need a mascot character like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:58.75,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuru-chan, are you in any other clubs?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.75,0:22:00.32,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... The calligraphy club.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:01.95,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit that then.
