Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:22.88,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did she just understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.88,0:22:25.87,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll quit the calligraphy club and join this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.87,0:22:30.10,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not sure what the literary club does...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.10,0:22:32.29,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't the literary club.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.85,0:22:36.01,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We're temporarily borrowing this room.
