Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.15,0:22:42.69,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...is an unnamed association yet to be made by Suzumiya over there that will participate in unknown activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.09,0:22:45.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, the person sitting there reading...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:47.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the real literary club member.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:50.20,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:52.24,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I just came up with a name!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.94,0:22:54.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:56.91,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Attention everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:22:59.96,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The name of this fledgling club has just been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:03.25,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,SOS Brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.97,0:23:09.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The save the world by overloading it with fun Haruhi Suzumiya's Brigade.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.74,0:23:12.40,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or SOS Brigade for short.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.40,0:23:13.97,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Feel free to laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.37,0:23:21.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Originally, it should have been the save the world by overloading it with fun Haruhi Suzumiya Association...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:24.81,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but an association hasn't even been formed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.81,0:23:27.57,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And nobody has a clue as to what this group is supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:29.53,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So brigade is fine then.
